| securitySchemes | Map\[`string`, [Security Scheme Object](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.0.html#security-scheme-object) | [Reference Object](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.0.html#reference-object)\] | An object to hold reusable [Security Scheme Objects](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.0.html#security-scheme-object). |
