| parameters | \[[Parameter Object](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#parameter-object) | [Reference Object](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#reference-object)\] | A list of parameters that are applicable for this operation. If a parameter is already defined at the [Path Item](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#pathItemParameters), the new definition will override it but can never remove it. The list *MUST NOT* include duplicated parameters. A unique parameter is defined by a combination of a [name](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#parameterName) and [location](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#parameterIn). The list can use the [Reference Object](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#reference-object) to link to parameters that are defined at

the [OpenAPI Object’s components/parameters](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.3.html#componentsParameters). |
